                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;   The SUSE Linux Enterprise 12 SP5 kernel was updated to receive various&lt;br/&gt;
   security and bugfixes.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;   The following security bug was fixed:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;CVE-2021-3348: Fixed a use-after-free read in nbd_queue_rq (bsc#1181504).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;   The following non-security bugs were fixed:&lt;br/&gt;
   &lt;a href=&quot;https://lists.suse.com/pipermail/sle-security-updates/2021-March/008460.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://lists.suse.com/pipermail/sle-security-updates/2021-March/008460.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
